name: Neo Null Space
description: Creates an 3x3x3 Null Space(Or adds 3x3x3to a Null Space), As long as this Insignia is active (10 Minutes) the Insignia cannot decay below 3 blocks, unless the original caster moves, for every block the caster moves, the Null Space decays 1 block, this also applies beyond 3x3x3.
